=============
= libmixmod =
=============

Core MIXMOD library: MIXture of (gaussian or multinomial) MODels.
Main features:
 > clustering (unsupervised classification)
 > supervised classification

----------------------------------------------------------------------

To build Mixmod on UNIX system, type in BUILD directory:

cd BUILD
cmake .. -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=$HOME/software/libmixmod
make install

To run applications that use libmixmod, append these lines to your ~/.bashrc:

export MIXMODDIR=$HOME/software/libmixmod
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$LD_LIBRARY_PATH:$MIXMODDIR/lib

And run `source ~/.bashrc` to apply the changes.
